title: Lakata and Hynek take stage three win in Cape Epic
text:
Lakata and Hynek take stage three win in Cape Epic 10:00am GMT - 02:47 
The yellow jersey changed hands in stage three of the Cape Epic mountain biking race on Wednesday and Austrian Alban Lakata and his Czech team mate Kristian Hynek took a hard-fought stage win ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
